5A1FE05B.Line1.6E261: The Overseers sent him to the prisons, of course. They laughed about the strange man all night. That was the last time they laughed.

6F2AC46C.Line11.6E261: I... I saw him at the royal court. He walked in, unannounced. (sigh) Demanded the city to be given to him.

C9294688.VoiceDir1.6E261: Very dark for the last sentence
